{"tid":2254673,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳智思：無興趣參加下屆行政長官選舉","createTime":"2020-10-23T04:13:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T06:15:32.000Z","uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"46fb30c4e4263c6a518803b6edd2f7117d5ed336","tid":2254673,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T04:13:01.000Z","msg":"行政會議召集人陳智思表示，絕對無興趣參加下屆行政長官選舉，因此如非必要，他不會在公開場合演說，以免社會產生太多陰謀論。陳智思早上出席「團結香港基金」網上論壇時表示，他認為特首作為領袖，最基本是同時獲香港市民及中央政府信任，亦要具備溝通能力，懂得分析及平衡不同議題。 <br />\n<br />\n陳智思又指，無可能每項政府政策都滿足到所有市民，有時會有矛盾，但強調當局是要平衡不同群組的利益，不只要滿足一人，亦要「擺平」其他持份者。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2362970\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2362970&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FRCPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=90e18c57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2362970</a>"},{"pid":"5e613b6eb3bfa109497a40d8ba11a582f6a94760","tid":2254673,"uid":47697,"like":9,"dislike":6,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T04:14:05.000Z","msg":"邊個做都死<br />\n咪又係聽阿爺話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08039303c6564df02c2d8beac01837b12e770972","tid":2254673,"uid":94241,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T04:14:11.000Z","msg":"個個行政長官做之前 都會話自己唔會做/無興趣架啦"},{"pid":"60c0b1b529226ca46a59f3d2eed74ac000c6458a","tid":2254673,"uid":231583,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T04:14:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe34d4685dbae48677bf0649faf1058ea5228044","tid":2254673,"uid":21470,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T04:15:33.000Z","msg":"689 : 無意選 》當選<br />\n777 : 無意選 》當選<br />\n1200: 無意選 》當選"},{"pid":"3966392d2b57e339e636f44134d2baece901ace9","tid":2254673,"uid":171849,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T04:15:42.000Z","msg":"當年林奠夠話唔選啦<br />\n最後CY話唔尋求連任<br />\n下秒即刻話上帝叫佢選<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\"